Hello,
{pp}
I was wondering if AIO or readers know much about the different models of
A1200s.  As I have 2 and they both seem to have different downfalls.
One has a wierd AGA chipset, which won't allow me to view dblPAL or modes
like that, that are used for SVGA monitors etc..  And the other has a
serial port that cannot connect above 56Kbps or it will just get constant
errors.  I haven't got the first one with me at the moment, but the other
model is 1.4.D.
{pp}
Just wondering if there was actually a model of the A1200 made, that works
100% :)
{pp}
Also, clock ports seem to differ from model to model.
{pp}
Cyas later, thanks in advance for any help.
{pp}
-Splatt
